Class Attribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jsoup.nodes.Attribute
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class Attribute
extends Object
implements Map.Entry<String,String>, Cloneable
    A single key + value attribute. Keys are trimmed and normalised to lower-case.
